author: kwright
msg: Add hook that allows API access to arbitrary connector logic.  This is anticipated to be used for when external UI's are developed that need connector support for presenting lists of (for example) child folders.  I therefore added it only to the output and repository connectors, since only these two connector types have connector-specific specifications.
